Who are its clients?

TaskUs works primarily with technology and digital-first companies in areas such as:

Social media
E-commerce
Gaming
Streaming media
Financial services
Healthcare
Artificial intelligence and autonomous vehicles

Publicly mentioned clients and partners have included Meta, DoorDash, Netflix, Chime, and Waymo.

Why is TaskUs well known?

TaskUs differentiates itself from traditional call-center companies by focusing on:

Digital-first customer support
Cloud-based operations
Content moderation and online safety
AI operations and training data services
A strong employee-focused culture ("Be Ridiculous" is one of its core values)

